members.name: DEFAULT_VALUE
members.comment: The default value, returned by the default action.

members.name: defaultAction
members.comment: The default action, used by all visit methods that are not overridden.

param: p - the parameter value passed to the visit method
return: the result value to be returned from the visit method

members.name: visit
members.comment: Invokes the appropriate visit method specific to the type of the node.

param: node - the node on which to dispatch
p - a parameter to be passed to the appropriate visit method
return: the value returns from the appropriate visit method

members.name: visit
members.comment: Invokes the appropriate visit method on each of a sequence of nodes.

param: nodes - the nodes on which to dispatch
p - a parameter value to be passed to each appropriate visit method
return: the value return from the last of the visit methods, or null if none were called
